## ⚙️ PHẦN 3: KHỐI 2 - TỐI ƯU BACKEND

### Lựa chọn: **whisper.cpp** (Primary) + **Piper TTS** (C++ native)

| Tiêu chí | whisper.cpp | sherpa-onnx |
|-----------|-------------|-------------|
| ARM NEON SIMD | ✅ Tự động detect & dùng | ✅ Qua ONNX Runtime |
| GGUF Quantization | ✅ Native support | ❌ Dùng ONNX format |
| Latency trên Pi5 | ⚡ Rất thấp | ⚡ Thấp |
| Memory footprint | ~50MB total | ~80-100MB |
| Build complexity | Đơn giản (CMake) | Phức tạp hơn |
| **Verdict** | **✅ CHỌN** | Backup option |

### Build whisper.cpp cho Pi5 (ARM NEON):

```bash
# Build với ARM NEON optimization
cd whisper.cpp
mkdir build && cd build
cmake .. \
  -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release \
  -DWHISPER_NO_ACCELERATE=ON \
  -DCMAKE_CXX_FLAGS="-march=armv8.2-a+dotprod -O3 -ftree-vectorize"
make -j4

# Python binding
pip install whispercpp  # hoặc build từ source
```

### Build Piper TTS:

```bash
# Piper đã có pre-built binary cho ARM64
wget https://github.com/rhasspy/piper/releases/download/v1.2.0/piper_arm64.tar.gz
tar xzf piper_arm64.tar.gz

# Download Vietnamese voice model
wget https://huggingface.co/rhasspy/piper-voices/resolve/main/vi/vi_VN-vais1000-medium.onnx
```

